{
  "stem": "2533.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I just want to get away to-- to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I've got an address to Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I knew the people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't understand me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was an elderly gentleman was sitting behind a very big desk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he couldn't understand me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the secretary came in, and she was so angry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did I get in there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, a gentleman told-- called me in because the door was open.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what do I want?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wanted to know what I want.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said-- so I told her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I gave him the address.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He didn't ask for papers-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he took out a sheet of paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He wrote something, put the stamp on, and he said to go with those-- with that paper to Krochmalna Street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There is a-- a-- not a-- it was almost like a camp, but a transit place, the people who were going to Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And to wait there for a day or two, and I'll get all my papers, the ticket and some food, and I will be off to Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was when I left Lublin--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he didn't ask.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing I said that I want to go as a volunteer worker to Germany, and I have an address to Frankfurt on Main, and the name of the people I'm going there, because they're already working there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe there was on the address was the place where they were working, but I didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all, you know-- and I understood what that girl told him in German, because I understood German.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could even speak, but I couldn't let on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because at that time of-- when I-- when they were teaching German at school, I was too young.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
